      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a collector-grade find that looks and feels as though it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like shine with zero scratches, dents, or chips. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the leather remains supple and free of any wear, and every electronic feature functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and meticulously maintained with a full service history. Buyers can expect a showroom-quality vehicle that requires nothing but a new owner to appreciate its perfect state.",
