    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable daily driver that's perfect for your commute! This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and offers a fantastic balance of reliability and value. While you'll notice some expected signs of wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a solid performer that\u2019s ready to get you where you need to go. It's a great opportunity to own a functional, hardworking car at a price that makes sense!",
