    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is currently in running order. While the engine starts and the car is drivable, it shows its age with some visible body wear, minor surface rust, and an interior that would benefit from a deep clean. Mechanically, it is functional, though a routine service and attention to some minor oil seeps are recommended for long-term reliability. This is a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable daily driver that they can improve over time.",
