    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-maintained and still has plenty of life left for all your weekend adventures or daily commutes. It looks great and runs even better! I\u2019m looking for someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 34500.0,
